Package: lipidAnnotator
Title: Parse and Annotate Lipid Names with LIPID MAPS Classification
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: 
    person("David", "Guardamino Ojeda", 
           email = "david.guardamino@gmail.com", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Parses lipid names in any format and annotates them with LIPID MAPS 
    canonical classification, shorthand notation per Liebisch et al. (2020), 
    and structural metadata including ether linkage, sphingoid base prefix, 
    and annotation level.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
Suggests: testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
URL: https://github.com/DavidGO464/lipidAnnotator , https://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.19336739
BugReports: https://github.com/DavidGO464/lipidAnnotator/issues
